'''短脚鹎属'''（[[屬名|屬名]]：{{lang|la|''Hypsipetes''}}，由[[古希臘文|古希臘文]]的 {{lang|gre|ὕψῐ}} / ''hypsi'' 與 {{lang|gre|πετής}} / ''pétēs'' 轉寫而成，意為「高飛者」<ref name = Jobling>{{ cite book | author = Jobling, J. A. | title = ''Helm Dictionary of Scientific Bird Names'' | url = https://archive.org/details/helmdictionarysc00jobl | publisher = Helm | year = 2010 | isbn = 978-1-4081-2501-4 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/helmdictionarysc00jobl/page/n200 200] }}</ref>）是[[雀形目|雀形目]][[鵯科|鵯科]]的一個[[屬|屬]]，屬於中小型[[鳴禽|鳴禽]]，羽色多為欖綠色、灰色或黑色調，嘴喙較大部分鵯科鳥類筆直，前端略為下彎，部分物種具有尖形的羽冠<ref name = Dickinson2002>{{cite journal | authors = Dickinson, E. C.; Gregory, S. M. S. | title = Systematic notes on Asian birds. 24. On the priority of the name ''Hypsipetes'' Vigors, 1831, and the division of the broad genus of that name | journal = ''Zoologische Verhandelingen'' | issn = 0024-1652 | year = 2002 | volume = 340 | pages = 75-91 | doi =  | url = https://repository.naturalis.nl/pub/220204 | access-date = 2021-04-22 | archive-date = 2021-04-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210426110202/https://repository.naturalis.nl/pub/220204/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{ cite journal | author = 張瑞麟 等 | title = 認識鵯科鳥類 | journal = 冠羽 | volume = 210 | pages = 4-6 | year = 2018年12月 | oclc = 859163065 | url = https://issuu.com/wildbirdtapei/docs/__210_ }}</ref>。短腳鵯屬成員主要分布於[[季風亞洲|季風亞洲]]，以及[[印度洋|西印度洋]]的[[馬達加斯加|馬達加斯加]]與鄰近島嶼，一些可能屬於這個屬的物種則還分布於{{le|華萊士區|Wallacea}}<ref name = Shakya2017>{{cite journal | authors = Shakya, S. B.; Sheldon, F. H. | title = The phylogeny of the world's bulbuls (Pycnonotidae) inferred using a supermatrix approach | journal = ''Ibis'' | issn = 1474-919X | year = 2017 | volume = 159 | issue = 3 | pages = 498-509 | doi = 10.1111/ibi.12464 | url = https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/full/10.1111/ibi.12464 | access-date = 2021-04-22 | archive-date = 2021-04-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210422155036/https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/full/10.1111/ibi.12464 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

